twoColConflict-explainconflict:
{{doc-important|The "editor" here refers to the editor softwares/extensions/features such as Wikitext editor, VisualEditor, ... etc. Not a random user who edited some pages.}}
Appears at the top of a page when there is an edit conflict.

Parameters:
$1 - Label of the save button. Either {{msg-mw|savechanges}} or {{msg-mw|publishchanges}}.

See also:
* {{msg-mw|Explainconflict}}
* {{msg-mw|Savearticle}}

